<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定也會增加！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是<delay20 />我做的<delay8 />
