<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要好好珍惜唷。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外<delay8 />還有一件事<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是<tag a="110" b="10" />的<delay8 />小建議。<10_4 />
