<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道南瓜<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有不同顏色嗎？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算你目前沒有不同顏色的南瓜，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只要大量種植，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我相信總有一天<delay8 />
